longBusinessSummary: Horizon Acquisition Corporation does not have significant operations. The company intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It focuses on pursuing opportunities in financial, technology and business services sectors. The company was formerly known as EAC Holdings Inc. Horizon Acquisition Corporation was incorporated in 2020 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut.
